<P>
   GADGETS-COLUMN _ The newest wrinkle in movie sound systems is
Dolby Digital 6.1 Extended Surround, which requires seven speakers
to bring the movie theater sound experience home. Sherwood America,
a California-based home and car audio specialist, won an Innovation
Award at the International Consumer Electronics Show in January for
its design of the Newcastle R-956 receiver, which is capable of
reproducing the 6.1 channel movie theater sound environment at
home. (Cummings, Dayton Daily News). 15. WITH PHOTO. MOVED.
</P>
