<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 2000-06-18 21:59 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A7756 &Cx1f; tta-z
u a BC-NY-EGAN-INSTALL-ART-2     06-18 0965
